 Enhanced controls:
 
 Joypad
   * 2nd button / blue: pause/select item (alongside with spacebar)
   * rev/fwd: set preset passwords in "enter certificate" screen
   * yellow: enter CUSTOM certificate if present (like TAB)
   * green/third button: toggle music on/off (like CTRL+S)
   * rev+fwd+play (hold several seconds): give up current game
   * rev+fwd+play+red: quit to workbench

 Keyboard
   * TAB: recall password contained in "CUSTOM" option/tooltype
   * function keys F2-F8 enter valid preset passwords for levels 2 => 8
   * F9 key restarts the game